{"tid":1262361,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【重開】其實香港有好多值得尊敬既英雄","createTime":"2019-06-27T15:58:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T07:48:17.000Z","uid":24284,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"360041b6cc7ac04fce2ebcb4f83b10633ae26d31","tid":1262361,"uid":24284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T15:58:54.000Z","msg":"除左太古梁烈士、香港女兒謝婉雯醫生<br />\n仲有馬尼拉人質事件英雄：謝廷駿、傅卓仁、梁錦榮<br />\n牛頭角大火：高級消防隊長張耀升、消防隊目許志傑<br />\n吊手岩救休班狗：消防隊目邱少明<br />\n等等等等，請各位補充<br />\n<br />\n每一個民族都有一日紀念佢地既英雄，我地應該每年定一日去拜祭，香港人就應該要紀念香港英雄<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nGlory to the heroes, Glory to Hong Kong! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbd52dad300d5612295bc16db11adcab134b0080","tid":1262361,"uid":24284,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T16:03:10.000Z","msg":"每年搵一日公眾假期，大家犧牲一日時間<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29645088c64fd847ef522fd294e42d96339d5411","tid":1262361,"uid":267120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T16:08:12.000Z","msg":"謝婉雯醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n消防員陳兆龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d5eb3a5a9752af51299c9a4f60b4f7a600fea95","tid":1262361,"uid":24284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T16:14:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9945486078f98a0d14ade06e98587cdc90e28a84","tid":1262361,"uid":24284,"like":0,"dislike"